### HOST
usbip list -l
#### example output
 - busid 1-1.1 (320f:5044)
   unknown vendor : unknown product (320f:5044)

 - busid 1-1.3 (045e:0745)
   Microsoft Corp. : Nano Transceiver v1.0 for Bluetooth (045e:0745)

 - busid 2-2 (1058:25fa)
   Western Digital Technologies, Inc. : unknown product (1058:25fa)
#### end example output
sudo usbip bind --busid=2-2
sudo usbipd


###  CLIENT
sudo modprobe vhci-hcd
sudo usbip attach --remote=192.168.1.212 --device=2-2
